owl:Ontology.terms:title: ERA vocabulary
owl:Ontology.rdfs:comment: Vocabulary defined by the European Union Agency for Railways to describe the concepts and relationships related to the European railway infrastructure and the vehicles authorized to operate over it.
owl:Ontology.rdfs:label: ERA vocabulary

owl:AnnotationProperty.rdfs:comment: Index code used in the original definition of a parameter in ERATV.
owl:AnnotationProperty.rdfs:label: eratv index

owl:AnnotationProperty.rdfs:comment: Index code used in the original definition of a parameter in RINF.
owl:AnnotationProperty.rdfs:label: rinf index

owl:AnnotationProperty.rdfs:comment: The WGS84 altitude of a SpatialThing (decimal meters above the local reference ellipsoid).
owl:AnnotationProperty.rdfs:label: altitude

owl:AnnotationProperty.rdfs:comment: The WGS84 latitude of a SpatialThing (decimal degrees).
owl:AnnotationProperty.rdfs:label: latitude

owl:AnnotationProperty.rdfs:comment: The WGS84 longitude of a SpatialThing (decimal degrees).
owl:AnnotationProperty.rdfs:label: longitude

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Existence and TSI compliance of rules for magnetic fields emitted by a vehicle.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: TSI mangnetic fields

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Existence and TSI compliance of limits in harmonics in the traction current of vehicles.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: TSI traction harmonics

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the country(ies) in where a vehicle type has been authorized to operate.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: authorized country

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Axle bearing condition monitoring.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: axle bearing condition monitoring

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Vehicle category.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: vehicle category

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Contact line system present in the section of line.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: contact line system

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication of the type of the contact line system
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: contact line system type

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication of which contact strip materials are permitted to be used.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: contact strip material

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Data SIM Card GSM-R Home Network
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: data GSM-R network

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Radio requirements used for demonstrating technical compatibility data
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: data radio compatible

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Use of eddy current brakes.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: eddy current braking

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: References the first topological object in an oriented relation.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: element A

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: References the second topological object in an oriented relation.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: element B

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: References the topology object of a higher-granularity level which contains a lower-granularity topology object.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: element part

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Type of end coupling (indicating tensile and compressive forces).
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: end coupling type

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: References the geolocation of the end of a tunnel.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: end location

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication of the traction supply system (nominal voltage and frequency).
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: energy supply system

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: ETCS baseline installed lineside/on-board
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: etcs base line

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: ERTMS / ETCS application level for degraded situation related to the track side equipment.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: ETCS level for degraded situation

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: ETCS equipment on-board and its level.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: ETCS equipment level

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Information about installed trackside/on-board equipment capable to transmit infill information by loop or GSM-R for level 1 installation.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: ETCS infill

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: ETCS level available in the section of line.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: etcs level

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: ERTMS / ETCS application level which expresses the possible operating relationships between track and train
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: etcs level type

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: ETCS M_version according to SRS 7.5.1.9.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: ETCS M_version

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: ETCS requirements used for demonstrating technical compatibility.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: ETCS system compatibility

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Fire safety category for tunnels.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: fire safety category

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Railway Freight Corridor that the line is designated to.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: freight corridor

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Section with train detection limitation, specific for route compatibility check on French network.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: french train detection system limitation

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Gauges as defined in European standard or other local gauges, including lower or upper part.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: gauging profile

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Number of active GSM-R mobiles (EDOR) or simultaneous communication session on-board for ETCS Level 2 (or level 3) needed to perform radio block centre handovers without having an operational disruption.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: GSM-R active mobiles

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Use of optional GSM-R functions which might improve operation on the line. They are for information only and not for network access criteria.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: GSM-R optional functions

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: GSM-R Radio Data communication on board and its Baseline.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: GSM-R radio data communication

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: GSM-R version installed lineside/on-board.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: GSM-R version

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: GSM-R networks covered by a roaming agreement
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: GSM-R network coverage

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Property that links a physical entity with its topological abstraction representation.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has abstraction

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Property that links a topological abstraction entity with its physical representation.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has implementation

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: References a signal associated with a topology object.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has signal

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the country in which an entity resides.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: in country

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication of radio legacy systems installed
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: legacy radio system

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Classification of a line according to the INF TSI.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: line category

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Related national railway line.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: line national ID

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates a relationship with a national railway line at a specific kilometer point.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: line referece

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A combination of the line category and speed at the weakest point of the track.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: load capability

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Use of magnetic brakes.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: magnetic braking

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Vehicle manufacturer company.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: manufacturer

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the country in which a vehicle or vehicle type is manufactured.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: manufacturing country

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Maximum amount of sand accepted on the track within value of sanding output for 30s, given in grams.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: max sanding output

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Combination of maximum speed and maximum cant deficiency for which the vehicle was assessed.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: maximum speed and cant deficiency

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Minimum permitted axle load per category of Vehicle, given in tons depending of the category of vehicle.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: min axle load per vehicle category

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the navigation possibilities between two related topological objects.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: navigability

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: References an associated topological object.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: net element

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Reference to a property that is not applicable.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: not applicable

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Reference to a property that is not yet available.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: not yet available

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Operational Point at the end of a Section of Line.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: OP end

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Operational Point at the start of a Section of Line.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: OP start

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the type on an operational point.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: operational point type

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates an operational restriction of vehicle or wagon.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: operational restriction

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Other train protection, control and warning systems for degraded situation.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: other train protection

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication of which TSI compliant pantograph heads are allowed to be used.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: tsi pantograph head

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Parking brake type (if the vehicle is fitted with it).
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: parking brake type

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: References a tunnel that a track goes through.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: passes through tunnel

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Reference to a related platform.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: platform

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Distance between the upper surface of platform and running surface of the neighbouring track. It is the nominal value expressed in millimetres.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: platform height

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Determines the position of the topological object A in a relation.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: position on A

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Determines the position of the topological object B in a relation.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: position on B

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Coding for combined transport for semi-trailers as defined in UIC Code.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: profile number for semi-trailers

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Coding for combined transport with swap bodies as defined in UIC Code.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: profile number for swap bodies

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication of which class B system is installed
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: protection legacy system

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Country where a vehicle may operate without noise restrictions
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: quieter route exempted country

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: An angle defining the inclination of the head of a rail relative to the running surface.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: rail inclination

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Applicable rolling stock fire category for a tunnel.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: rolling stock fire category

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Reference to a related siding.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: siding

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Snow, ice and hail conditions.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: snow ice hail conditions

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the nature of a section of line.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: section of line nature

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: References the geolocation of the start of a tunnel.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: start location

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Vehicle subcategory.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: vehicle subcategory

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Platform height for which the vehicle is designed.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: supported platform height

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the related TEN (trans-European network).
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: TEN classification

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Reference case of a TSI thermal capacity.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: thermal capacity TSI reference

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Reference to a related railway track.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: track

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Track normal running direction.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: track direction

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Train detection systems installed in the section of line.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: train detection system

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Type of track circuits or axle counter to which specific checks are needed.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: detection system specific check

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication of supported types of train detection systems.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: train detection system type

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: TSI compliance of rules on the use of composite brake blocks.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: TSI compliant composite brake blocks

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: TSI compliance of Ferromagnetic characteristics of wheel material required.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: TSI compliant ferromagnetic wheel material

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether required distance between two consecutive axles is compliant with the TSI.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: TSI compliant max distance consecutive axles

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: TSI compliance of maximum permitted impedance between opposite wheels of a wheelset.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: TSI compliant max impedance wheelset

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: TSI compliance of rules for vehicle metal construction.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: TSI compliant metal construction

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: TSI compliance of rules for metal-free space around wheels.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: TSI compliant metal free space

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: TSI compliance of rules on combination of RST characteristics influencing shunting impedance.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: TSI compliant RST shunt impedance

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: TSI Compliance of rules on sand characteristics.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: TSI compliant sand characteristics

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: TSI compliance of sanding rules to allow compatibility with track circuits. Too much sand brings the risk of not detecting trains in tracks equipped with track circuits.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: TSI compliant sanding

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: TSI compliance of rules on shunt assisting devices.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: TSI compliant shunt devices

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the organization that owns/operated a vehicle or wagon.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: vehicle keeper

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the vehicle type of a specific vehicle or wagon.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: vehicle type

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Voice SIM Card GSM-R Home Network
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: voice GSM-R network

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Radio requirements used for demonstrating technical compatibility voice
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: voice radio compatible

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A single value expressed in millimetres that identifies the track and vehicle wheel set gauge.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: wheel set gauge

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Wheelset gauge changeover facility.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: wheelset gauge changeover facility

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Existence of limit for acceleration of train if stopping or recovering speed close to a level crossing expressed in a specific reference acceleration curve.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: acceleration allowed level crossings

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Electronic document available in two EU languages from the IM stored by the Agency providing additional information as defined in point (2) of point 4.2.2.6.2 of the Annex to Regulation XXX - OPE TSI.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: additional braking information document

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Alternative name of a vehicle.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: alternative name

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Altitude range.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: altitude range

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Altitude range value for 'X' if value 'AX' is selected in altitude range.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: altitude range detail

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Information of the train access level for which the boarding aid can be used. Data is presented as the vertical difference that is overcome by the platform boarding aid in millimetres. The value 0 means that the platform is not equipped with a platform boarding aid.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: area boarding aid

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication of existence of equipment or staff supporting the train crew in starting the train.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: assistance starting train

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication of whether an automatic dropping device (ADD) required on the vehicle.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: automatic dropping device required

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Position of the axles along the unit. a: Distance between axles; b: Distance from end axle to the end of the nearest coupling plane; c: distance between two inside axles.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: axle spacing

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Description of any integrated boarding aids (if provided).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: boarding aids

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Brake weight percentage (lambda) or Braked mass.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: brake weight percentage

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Cant deficiency (maximum uncompensated lateral acceleration) for which the vehicle has been assessed. For dual gauge vehicles values for each gauge have to be indicated.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: cant defficiency

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Maximum cant deficiency expressed in millimetres defined as difference between the applied cant and a higher equilibrium cant the line has been designed for.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: cant deficiency

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Maximum rated current from the catenary (to be indicated for each electrical energy supply system the vehicle is equipped for), given in A.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: catenary max rated current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Document with the procedure(s) for static and dynamic route compatibility checks.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: structure check document

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Compliance of the tunnel with INF TSI at the maximum permitted speed.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: compliance with INF TSI

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates if a vehicle's composite brake block is retrofitted
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: composite brake block retrofitted

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Regenerative braking allowed under certain conditions.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: conditional regenerative brake

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Conditions of use regarding train formation.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: conditions train formation

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Smallest cross section area in square metres of the tunnel.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: cross section area

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication of whether an on board current or power limitation function on vehicles is required.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: current limitation required

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Dangerous goods for which the vehicle is suitable (tank code).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: dangerous goods tank code

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Unique number for EI declarations concerning requirements of ENE (ENErgy subsytem) on the specific track.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: declaration of demonstration ENE

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Unique number for EI declarations concerning requirements of INF (INFrastructure) TSI.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: declaration of demonstration INF

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Unique number for EI declarations concerning requirements of SRT (Safety in Railway Tunnels) TSI for infrastructure system.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: declaration of demonstration SRT

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Design mass under exceptional payload.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: design mass under exceptional payload

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Design mass under normal payload.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: design mass under normal payload

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Design mass in working order.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: design mass in working order

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether it is allowed to use diesel or other thermal traction in the tunnel.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: diesel thermal allowed

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Distance between the signboard authorizing the driver to raise pantograph or close the circuit breaker after passing the phase separation and the end of the phase separation section. Specific for route compatibility check on French network.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: distance sign and phase

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Number of driving cabs. For wagons the number of driving cabs is to be set to zero (0).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: driving cabs

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Possibility of preventing the use of the eddy current track brake (only if fitted with eddy current brake)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: eddy current brake prevention

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Document with the conditions for the use of eddy current brakes.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: eddy current braking conditions document

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Stopping distance and deceleration profile for each load condition per design maximum speed.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: emergency braking

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the coordinate point where a linear object ends.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: end intrinsic coordinate

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: TSI conform energy meter for billing purposes installed on board.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: energy meter installed

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Maximum power (to be indicated for each energy supply system the vehicle is equipped for), given in kW.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: energy supply max power

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication if the traction supply system (nominal voltage and frequency) is fully compliant with TSI.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: energy supply system TSI compliant

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Data communication application for ETCS implementation.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: ETCS data communication application

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether infill is required to access the line for safety reasons.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: ETCS infill line access

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: ETCS national applications implemented (NID_XUSER of Packet 44).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: ETCS national applications

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether data for national packet 44 applications is transmitted between track and train.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: ETCS national packet 44

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: ETCS on-board implementation.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: ETCS on-board implementation

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Optional ETCS functions which might improve operation on the line.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: ETCS optional functions

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Wheel material is ferromagnetic.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: ferromagnetic wheel material

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Number of fixed seats.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: fixed seats

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether the use of on-board device for flange lubrication is forbidden
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: flange lube forbidden

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether rules for activation or deactivation of flange lubrication exist.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: flange lube rules

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates if the vehicle type is fitted for flange lubrication.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: flange lubrication fitted

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Location of particular points requiring specific checks due to deviations from gauging. The location (generally the distance from the origin of the line to the centre) on a line is given in kilometres with decimals (precision of 0.001).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: gauging check location

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Document with the transversal section of the particular points requiring specific checks.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: gauging traversal document

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication if GPRS can be used for ETCS.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: GPRS for ETCS

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication of the area in which GPRS can be used for ETCS.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: GPRS implementation area

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Maximum value of the gradient for stabling tracks expressed in millimetres per metre.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: gradient

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Sequence of gradient values and locations of change in gradient.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: gradient profile

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Any additional information on network characteristics or corresponding document available from the IM and stored by the Agency, e.g.; interference level, leading to the recommendation of additional on-board protection.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: GSM-R additional network info

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication if there is no GSMR coverage.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: GSM-R no coverage

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Number of GSM-R mobile sets in driving cab for data transmission.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: GSM-R sets in driving cab

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Availability by the IM of additional information as defined in 4.2.2.6.2 (2) Regulation XXX - OPE TSI.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has additional braking information

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Automatic dropping device (ADD) fitted (to be indicated for each energy supply system the vehicle is equipped for).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has automatic dropping device

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Specifies whether track construction is with sleepers embedded in ballast or not..
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has ballast

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Vehicle equipped with a cant deficiency compensation system (tilting vehicle).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has cant defficiency compensation

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Electric units equipped with power or current limitation function.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has current limitation

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether restrictions or conditions due to partial compliance with the CCS TSI exist.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has ETCS restrictions conditions

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether an installation for electric shore supply exists (fixed installation for servicing trains).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has electric shore supply

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether emergency plan exists.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has emergency plan

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether exists an installation for external cleaning facility (fixed installation for servicing trains) as defined in INF TSIs.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has external cleaning

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Existence of trackside hot axle box detector (HABD).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has axle box detector

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether level crossings (including pedestrian track crossing) exist on the section of line.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has level crossings

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Possibility of preventing the use of the lubrication device (only if fitted with flange lubrication).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has lubrication device prevention

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication if other train protection, control and warning systems in normal operation are installed lineside.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has other train protection

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates if a vehicle type has parking brake.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has parking brake

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether exists an installation for refuelling (fixed installation for servicing trains) as defined in INF TSIs.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has refuelling

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether regenerative braking is permitted or not.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has regenerative brake

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether an installation for sand restocking exists (fixed installation for servicing trains).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has sand restocking

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Possibility of preventing the use of sanding.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has sanding prevention

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Climatic conditions on the line are severe according to European standard.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has severe weather conditions

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the presence of shunting restrictions.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has shunting restrictions

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication of existence of system separation.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has system separation

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication if there is any train detection system installed and fully compliant with the CCS TSI requirements.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has TSI train detection

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication whether exists an installation for toilet discharge (fixed installation for servicing trains) as defined in INF TSIs.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has toilet discharge

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indication of on-board management system about completeness of the train information.

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: An operational point (OP) means any location for train service operations, where train services may begin and end or change route, and where passenger or freight services may be provided; operational point also means any location at boundaries between Member States or infrastructure managers.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Operational Point

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Platform for the purpose of RINF is understood as a platform edge. A platform concerns only the part of the structure neighbouring to the track (interfaced with trains).
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Platform

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A section of line means the part of line between adjacent operational points and may consist of several tracks.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Section Of Line

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Sidings are all those tracks where running trains in service movements ends and which are not used for operational routing of a train.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Siding

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A railway signal is an installation next to the railway track for signalling the maximum allowed speed in the next block section to the train driver.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Signal

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A running track that is used for train service movements.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Track

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: System used to detect the position of vehicles in the railway track.

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A railway tunnel is an excavation or a construction around the track provided to allow the railway to pass for example higher land, buildings or water.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Tunnel

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A specific vehicle or wagon able to operate over railway lines.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Vehicle

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A company or organization that owns or operates a certain vehicle.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Vehicle Keeper

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A vehicle type that has been authorized to operate on the EU railway infrastructure.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Vehicle Type

owl:Class.rdfs:comment:
Uniquely identified by lat/long/alt. i.e.
spaciallyIntersects(P1, P2) :- lat(P1, LAT), long(P1, LONG), alt(P1, ALT), lat(P2, LAT), long(P2, LONG), alt(P2, ALT).
sameThing(P1, P2) :- type(P1, Point), type(P2, Point), spaciallyIntersects(P1, P2).
A point, typically described using a coordinate system relative to Earth, such as WGS84.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: point

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Anything with spatial extent, i.e. size, shape, or position. e.g. people, places, bowling balls, as well as abstract areas like cubes.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: SpatialThing

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: geo

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A comma-separated representation of a latitude, longitude coordinate.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: lat/long

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The relation between something and the point, or other geometrical thing in space, where it is. For example, the realtionship between a radio tower and a Point with a given lat and long. Or a relationship between a park and its outline as a closed arc of points, or a road and its location as a arc (a sequence of points). Clearly in practice there will be limit to the accuracy of any such statement, but one would expect an accuracy appropriate for the size of the object and uses such as mapping .
